ed="T" n="0830b16"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0830b16"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName><persName key="A012339">亡名</persName><ptr target="#n2485"/>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0830b17"/><persName key="A012339"><persName>釋天竺</persName><persName>亡名</persName></persName>，未詳何<placeName key="PL000000048207">印度</placeName>人也。其貌惡陋，<lb
ed="T" n="0830b18"/>纏乾陀色<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1702"/>縵條衣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g878"/>，穿革屣，曳鐵錫，化行于<lb
ed="T" n="0830b19"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京輦</ref>。當<persName key="A004370"><persName>韋</persName><persName>南康</persName><persName>臯</persName></persName>之生也，纔三日<ptr target="#n542"/>，其家召<lb
ed="T" n="0830b20"/>僧齋，<ref type="person" target="#A012339">此僧</ref>不速自來──其日僧必歷寺連名<lb
ed="T" n="0830b21"/>請至──，<name>韋</name>氏家僮患其長一人，甚怒之，以弊<lb
ed="T" n="0830b22"/>席坐于庭中。既而齋畢，<name>韋</name>氏令乳母負嬰<lb
ed="T" n="0830b23"/>兒出，意請眾僧祝願焉。<ref type="person" target="#A012339"><name>梵</name>僧</ref>先從座起，攝<lb
ed="T" n="0830b24"/>衣升階，視之曰：「別久無恙乎？」嬰兒若有喜<lb
ed="T" n="0830b25"/>色相認之意。眾皆異之。<persName key="A023601">韋<roleName>君</roleName></persName><ptr target="#n2486"/>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A004370">此子</ref>纔生三<lb
ed="T" n="0830b26"/>日，<ref type="person" target="#A012339">吾師</ref>何言別久也？」<ref type="person" target="#A012339"><name>梵</name>僧</ref>曰：「此非檀越所<lb
ed="T" n="0830b27"/>知也。」<persName key="A023601">韋<roleName>君</roleName></persName>固問之，<ref type="person" target="#A012339"><name>梵</name>僧</ref>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A004370">此子</ref>乃<persName key="A006071">諸葛亮</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0830b28"/>之後身耳。<persName key="A006071">武候</persName>鼎國時為<placeName key="PL000000000100">蜀</placeName>丞相，君所知<lb
ed="T" n="0830b29"/>也。緣<placeName key="PL000000000100">蜀</placeName>人受其賜且久，今降生於世，將<pb ed="T" n="0830c" xml:id="T50.2061.0830c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0830c01"/>為<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀</placeName>帥，必福坤維<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1492"/>之人。<ref type="person" target="#A012339">吾</ref>往在<placeName key="PL000000035743">劍門</placeName>，與<ref type="person" target="#A004370">此<lb
ed="T" n="0830c02"/>子</ref>為善友。既知其生于君門，<ref type="person" target="#A012339">吾</ref>不遠而來。<lb
ed="T" n="0830c03"/><ref type="person" target="#A004370">此子</ref>作<placeName key="PL000000034815">劍南</placeName>節度二十年，官極貴中書令、太<lb
ed="T" n="0830c04"/>尉。此外非<ref type="person" target="#A012339">我</ref>所知也。<ptr target="#n2487"/>」<ref type="person" target="#A023601">父</ref>然之，因以<persName key="A004370">武子</persName>為<lb
ed="T" n="0830c05"/>字，又單字<persName key="A004370">武</persName>也<ptr target="#n2490"/>。<persName key="A012340">張鎰</persName>出為<placeName key="PL000000042848">鳳翔</placeName><placeName key="PL000000042949">隴州</placeName>節度，<lb
ed="T" n="0830c06"/>奏<persName key="A004370">臯</persName>權知<placeName key="PL000000042949">隴州</placeName>。及<persName key="A012340">鎰</persName>為<persName key="A012341">李楚琳</persName>所殺，<persName key="A012342">牛雲<lb
ed="T" n="0830c07"/>光</persName>請<persName key="A004370">臯</persName>為帥。<persName key="A008866">朱泚</persName>不得已用<persName key="A004370">臯</persName>為<placeName key="PL000000042848">鳳翔</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0830c08"/><anchor xml:id="beg0830003"/>帥<anchor xml:id="end0830003"/><ptr target="#n2488"/>。<persName key="A004215">德宗</persName>置<placeName key="PL000000042949">奉義軍</placeName>節以旌之，續加禮部尚<lb
ed="T" n="0830c09"/>書<ptr target="#n2496"/>。<date notBefore-iso="+0784-01-31" key="j20074402007823" notAfter-iso="+0785-02-17"><name>興元</name>中</date>，駕還<placeName key="PL000000042189">京</placeName><ptr target="#n2489"/>，徵為左金吾衛將軍。<date from-iso="+0785-02-18" key="j20078242008178" to-iso="+0786-02-07"><name>貞<lb
ed="T" n="0830c10"/>元</name>元年</date>，為<placeName key="PL000000034805">成都</placeName>尹<ptr target="#n2491"/>，代<persName key="A012343">張延賞</persName>。到任和南蠻<lb
ed="T" n="0830c11"/>并戰功<ptr target="#n2492"/>，封<persName key="A004370">南康郡王</persName>。<persName key="A004380">順宗</persName>即位，進太尉<ptr target="#n2493"/>。<persName key="A004370">南<lb
ed="T" n="0830c12"/>康</persName>在任二十一年<ptr target="#n2497"/>，末塗甚崇<name>釋</name>氏──恒持數<lb
ed="T" n="0830c13"/>珠誦佛名。所養鸚鵡，教令念經。及死，焚<lb
ed="T" n="0830c14"/>之，有舍利焉<ptr target="#n1729"/>。<persName key="A004370">臯</persName>又歸心南宗禪道，學心法<lb
ed="T" n="0830c15"/>於<placeName key="PL000000034714">淨眾寺</placeName><persName key="A010304">神會<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>。在<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀</placeName>，富貴僭差<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1703"/>，重賦斂，<lb
ed="T" n="0830c16"/>時議非之<ptr target="#n2495"/>，然合<ref type="person" target="#A012339"><name>梵</name>僧</ref>懸記<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1165"/>焉。</p>
